---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - EngineeringExec" description="Privacy and cookie policy for engineeringexec.tech.">
  <div class="static-content">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy & Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 14, 2026</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Who I Am</h2>
    <p>This website, <strong>engineeringexec.tech</strong>, is a personal blog run by <strong>Michael Bleterman</strong>. It's a non-commercial project where I share thoughts on engineering leadership, software architecture, and R&D management.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong><br />
    You can reach me via the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/contact`}>Contact</a> page, or through my social profiles:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/michaelbleterman/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/michaelbleterman" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/michael.bleterman" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>For any privacy-related requests, please use the contact form on the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/contact`}>Contact</a> page with the subject "Privacy Request."</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>What Data I Collect and Why</h2>

    <h3>Website Analytics (Google Analytics)</h3>
    <p>I use <strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> to understand how visitors interact with this site — which pages are popular, how visitors find the site, and general usage patterns. This helps me improve the content.</p>
    <p><strong>Data collected:</strong> anonymized page views, approximate geographic region, device type, browser type, referring website, and session duration. Google Analytics may also collect your IP address, which Google processes in accordance with its own <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Your consent (via the cookie banner).</p>

    <h3>Social Sharing (ShareThis)</h3>
    <p>I use <strong>ShareThis</strong> to add social sharing buttons to blog posts.</p>
    <p><strong>Data collected:</strong> ShareThis may collect browsing data, device identifiers, and IP addresses for analytics and advertising purposes. You can review <a href="https://sharethis.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ShareThis's privacy policy</a> for details.</p>
    <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Your consent (via the cookie banner).</p>

    <h3>Contact Form</h3>
    <p>If you reach out through the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/contact`}>Contact</a> page, I collect the information you provide: your <strong>name</strong>, <strong>email address</strong>, and <strong>message</strong>.</p>
    <p><strong>Data collected:</strong> only what you voluntarily submit.</p>
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> to respond to your inquiry.</p>
    <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Your consent (by submitting the form). I will not use your contact information for marketing or share it with third parties.</p>

    <h3>Spam Protection (Google reCAPTCHA)</h3>
    <p>The contact form uses <strong>Google reCAPTCHA</strong> to prevent spam submissions.</p>
    <p><strong>Data collected:</strong> Google reCAPTCHA may collect hardware and software information, including device and application data, as described in <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's privacy policy</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interest (protecting the site from spam).</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Cookies</h2>

    <h3>What Are Cookies?</h3>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your browser. They help websites function properly, remember your preferences, and understand usage patterns.</p>

    <h3>How This Site Uses Cookies</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Category</th>
          <th>Examples</th>
          <th>Purpose</th>
          <th>Default</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Necessary</strong></td>
          <td>CookieYes consent</td>
          <td>Site functionality and remembering your cookie preferences</td>
          <td>Always active</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Analytics</strong></td>
          <td>Google Analytics</td>
          <td>Understanding site traffic and visitor behavior</td>
          <td>Off until you consent</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Marketing</strong></td>
          <td>ShareThis</td>
          <td>Social sharing functionality and related analytics</td>
          <td>Off until you consent</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Functional</strong></td>
          <td>Google reCAPTCHA</td>
          <td>Spam protection on the contact form</td>
          <td>Off until you consent</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>On first visit:</strong> A cookie banner will ask for your consent. You can Accept All, Reject All, or Customise by category.</li>
      <li><strong>Change your mind:</strong> Click the cookie icon in the bottom-left corner of any page to reopen the consent panel and update your preferences at any time.</li>
      <li><strong>Browser settings:</strong> You can also block or delete cookies through your browser settings. Note that blocking essential cookies may affect site functionality.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Third-Party Cookies</h3>
    <p>Some cookies are set by third-party services (Google, ShareThis) that operate independently. I do not control these cookies. Please review their respective privacy policies linked above.</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>How Long I Keep Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Cookie consent records:</strong> retained for 12 months (managed by CookieYes), after which you will be asked to consent again.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> retained in Google Analytics for 14 months (Google's default), then automatically deleted.</li>
      <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> retained only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry, then deleted.</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under <strong>GDPR</strong> (if you're in the EU/EEA) and <strong>Israel's Privacy Protection Law</strong> (Amendment 13), you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of the personal data I hold about you</li>
      <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — ask me to correct inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — ask me to delete your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
      <li><strong>Restrict processing</strong> — ask me to limit how I use your data</li>
      <li><strong>Object</strong> — object to my processing of your data</li>
      <li><strong>Data portability</strong> — request your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
      <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> — withdraw your cookie consent at any time via the cookie settings icon, or contact me for other data</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, please reach out via the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/contact`}>Contact</a> page. I will respond within 30 days.</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>I do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data. Data is only shared with the third-party services listed above (Google Analytics, ShareThis, Google reCAPTCHA) as necessary for the purposes described. I do not share contact form submissions with anyone.</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This site is not directed at children under 16. I do not knowingly collect personal data from minors. If you believe a child has provided me with personal data, please contact me and I will promptly delete it.</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>I may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>
    <hr />

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy or how your data is handled, please reach out via the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')}/contact`}>Contact</a> page.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
